The '''Cherenkov effect''' was a visual effect produced by high amounts of hard [[Radiation/Legends|radiation]], taking the appearance of a [[Color/Legends|blue-colored]] flame. The effect could be triggered by the use of explosives such as [[Fusion bomb/Legends|fusion]] or [[anti-matter bomb]]s, and the radiation it accompanied was potentially deadly.

During the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]], [[Princess/Legends|Princess]] [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa]] observed the Cherenkov effect in the ruined city of [[K'avor]] on [[Shiva IV]], deducing the cause to have been an anti-matter bomb.

